skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tech alpharetta
des:
Tech Alpharetta’s mission remains the same–to help grow technology and innovation in Alpharetta

Tech Alpharetta skill will give information about upcoming events happening in the month. Here you can know about our members, our leaders and our mentors. And you can get answers for your questions related to how to join and about members in tech alpharetta.

Be Curious, ask Alexa to show me the tech alpharetta events

ASK AWAY: You can now get started by saying:
 - tech alpharetta, show me the events
 - tech alpharetta, how to contact you
 - tech alpharetta, tell me about you
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
